// AS3 linkage class `ScreenMatchSelect` is the openfl-swf generated library symbol `Screen_matchSelect` (the SWF symbol's
// library name was snake/lowerCamel; openfl names the class from it, not the AS3 linkage). Alias the
// two so `new ScreenMatchSelect()` constructs the real clip (with its named child instances), not an empty stub.
typedef ScreenMatchSelect = Screen_matchSelect;
